Posts.Content: Thibk5 wrote: I had biopsies on both breasts for microcalcifications on Wednesday. They said 2 to 5 business days for results. So today is the earliest possible day to get called. My phone just rang and the caller ID literally read "Breast Cancer". I am NOT kidding. Anyway it was a nonprofit looking for donations!!!! Talk about bad timing! This waiting is awful!
